A 3-year-old girl was mauled to death by two pit bulls on Saturday.It is reported that the incident happened in Helmsley Grove in the Cato Manor area of Durban around 17:10pm.Paramedics arrived at the family home and found the three-year-old-girl with life threatening injuries. Paramedics from various services worked fervently to save the life of the severely mauled child. Tragically, despite all their effort the little girl was declared dead at the scene.The exact detail to the incident and preceding events is still speculative.-TNA Reporter 